122Kg 7:20 And that is just what happened to him - he died, trampled to death by the people at the city gate. 
122Kg 8:1 Now Elisha had told the woman who lived in Shunem, whose son he had brought back to life, that the LORD was sending a famine on the land, which would last for seven years, and that she should leave with her family and go and live somewhere else. 
