131Ch 8:13 Beriah and Shema were heads of families that settled in the city of Aijalon and drove out the people who lived in the city of Gath. 
131Ch 8:14 Beriah's descendants included Ahio, Shashak, Jeremoth, 
131Ch 8:15 Zebadiah, Arad, Eder, 
131Ch 8:16 Michael, Ishpah, and Joha. 
