131Ch 8:20 Elienai, Zillethai, Eliel, 
131Ch 8:21 Adaiah, Beraiah, and Shimrath. 
131Ch 8:22 Shashak's descendants included Ishpan, Eber, Eliel, 
131Ch 8:23 Abdon, Zichri, Hanan, 
131Ch 8:24 Hananiah, Elam, Anthothijah, 
131Ch 8:25 Iphdeiah, and Penuel. 
131Ch 8:26 Jeroham's descendants included Shamsherai, Shehariah, Athaliah, 
