131Ch 8:29 Jeiel founded the city of Gibeon and settled there. His wife was named Maacah, 
131Ch 8:30 and his oldest son, Abdon. His other sons were Zur, Kish, Baal, Ner, Nadab, 
131Ch 8:31 Gedor, Ahio, Zechariah, 
131Ch 8:32 and Mikloth, the father of Shimeah. Their descendants lived in Jerusalem near other families of their clan. 
131Ch 8:33 Ner was the father of Kish, and Kish was the father of King Saul. Saul had four sons�� Jonathan, Malchishua, Abinadab, and Eshbaal. 
