15Ezr 7:2 son of Shallum, son of Zadok, son of Ahitub, 
15Ezr 7:3 son of Amariah, son of Azariah, son of Meraioth, 
15Ezr 7:4 son of Zerahiah, son of Uzzi, son of Bukki, 
15Ezr 7:5 son of Abishua, son of Phinehas, son of Eleazar, son of Aaron. 
15Ezr 7:6 Ezra was a scholar with a thorough knowledge of the Law which the LORD, the God of Israel, had given to Moses. Because Ezra had the blessing of the LORD his God, the emperor gave him everything he asked for. 
