16Neh 3:17 The following Levites rebuilt the next several sections of the wall�� Rehum son of Bani built the next section; Hashabiah, ruler of half of the Keilah District, built the next section on behalf of his district; 
16Neh 3:18 Bavvai son of Henadad, ruler of the other half of the Keilah District, built the next section; 
16Neh 3:19 Ezer son of Jeshua, ruler of Mizpah, built the next section in front of the armory, as far as the place where the wall turns; 
16Neh 3:20 Baruch son of Zabbai built the next section, as far as the entrance to the house of the High Priest Eliashib; 
16Neh 3:21 Meremoth, the son of Uriah and grandson of Hakkoz, built the next section, up to the far end of Eliashib's house. 
16Neh 3:22 The following priests rebuilt the next several sections of the wall�� Priests from the area around Jerusalem built the next section; 
16Neh 3:23 Benjamin and Hasshub built the next section, which was in front of their houses; Azariah, the son of Maaseiah and grandson of Ananiah, built the next section, which was in front of his house; 
16Neh 3:24 Binnui son of Henadad built the next section, from Azariah's house to the corner of the wall; 
